Trade/Device Name(s): Emit II Plus Cocaine Metabolite Assay
Regulation Name(s): Cocaine and cocaine metabolite test system
Instrument(s)/Platform(s): Beckman Coulter DxC 700 AU Clinical Chemistry Analyzer
Document Summary: FDA 510(k) summary for Emit II Plus Cocaine Metabolite Assay for qualitative and semiquantitative analysis of benzoylecgonine in human urine
Indications for Use Summary: For qualitative and semiquantitative analyses of benzoylecgonine (cocaine metabolite) in human urine at 150 or 300 ng/mL cutoffs; provides preliminary analytical test results on chemistry analyzers
